Welcome to my Github repository for my MODs for phpBB3.

*
* Precise Similar Topics II v1.1.3
* ========================================================================
*
* Description:
* This MOD will display a list of similar/related topics at the bottom of
* your threads, based on finding the most relevant matching Topic Titles.
